%% Máquina de Estados: MCP Connection
%% Referência: docs/blueprint/09-state-models.md

stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> disconnected

    disconnected : Sem conexão ativa
    connecting : Estabelecendo conexão (stdio/SSE)
    connected : Conexão ativa, tools registradas
    error : Falha — aguardando decisão
    reconnecting : Reconexão com backoff exponencial

    disconnected --> connecting : connectMCP(config)
    connecting --> connected : Conexão OK + tools listadas
    connecting --> error : Timeout / falha (maxRetries)
    connected --> error : Heartbeat falha
    connected --> disconnected : disconnectMCP()
    error --> reconnecting : Reconexão automática
    reconnecting --> connected : Reconexão OK
    reconnecting --> error : Todas tentativas falharam
    error --> disconnected : disconnectMCP() / destroy()

    note right of connected
        Tools MCP registradas no ToolExecutor
        Health check periódico ativo
    end note

    note right of reconnecting
        Backoff exponencial
        Tools removidas do ToolExecutor
        até reconexão
    end note

    note left of error
        isolateErrors: true →
        outras tools não afetadas
    end note
